<div class="visitor_chat">
  <div class="box">
    <div class="after-chat-buttons">
      <div class='btn btn-info btn-block' data-ng-click="startChat()">No</div>
      <div class='btn btn-info btn-block' data-ng-click="startChat()">I follow another religion</div>
      <div class='btn btn-info btn-block' data-ng-click="startChat()">I am not sure</div>
      <div class='btn btn-success btn-block' data-ng-click="startChat()">I want to start</div>
      <div class='btn btn-success btn-block' data-ng-click="startChat()">I am trying</div>
      <div class='btn btn-success btn-block' data-ng-click="startChat()">I am following you</div>
    </div>
    <div id='player'></div>
    <iframe frameborder='0' id='webpage' src='about:blank'></iframe>
  </div>
  <div id='chat'>
    <h1 class='special'>{{campaign_data.title}}</h1>

    <div>
      <div class='panel panel-default'>
        <div class='panel-heading'>
          <small class='text-muted'>Jesus Asks</small>
          <br>
          Will you follow me?
        </div>
        <div class='panel-body'>
          <div class='btn btn-info btn-block' id='start-btn' data-ng-click="startChat()">Start Chat</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id='myfriends'>
      <div class='panel panel-default'>
        <div class='panel-heading'>
          <p class='lead name_box'>
            Hey &nbsp;<span class='name'></span>.
          </p>
          <p>That's great you want to start to follow Jesus. Sometimes, it's easier to start something new when a friend is involved.</p>
          <p>Would you like to invite a friend to chat or would you rather talk with someone we know?</p>
        </div>
        <div class='panel-body'>
          <div class='btn btn-primary btn-block' id='invite-btn' data-ng-click="showNextStep('#myfriends', '#linkafriend', 3, 4)">Invite a Christian friend</div>
          <div class='btn btn-primary btn-block' data-ng-click="showNextStep('#myfriends', '#opconnect', 3, 5)">Find someone for me</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id='linkafriend'>
      <div class='panel panel-default'>
        <div class='panel-heading'>
          <p class='lead'>You can invite your friend by sharing the link below with them via Facebook.</p>
          <input class='form-control' id='link' onClick='this.select();' readonly='readonly' value='http://godchat.tv/u/06dEQ'>
        </div>
        <div class='panel-body'>
          <p class='new-article'>While you wait why not look through the article “Starting with God”, I have just loaded it into the media box to the left.</p>
          <p class='old-article'>While we wait for your friend, you can keep reading the "Starting with God" article.</p>
          <a class='btn btn-default btn-sm btn-block' id='findsomeone-btn' data-ng-click="showNextStep('#linkafriend', '#opconnect', 4, 5)">Find someone for me instead</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id='chatbox'>
      <h1 class='special'>{{campaign_data.title}} Chat</h1>
      <ul class='conversation'>
      </ul>
      <input class="form-control chat-input" placeholder="Message..." type="text" ng-enter="postMessage()" data-ng-model="chatMessage">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>